text: Frederic Schenck (October 10, 1887 - February 28, 1919) was an American fencer. He competed in the individual épée event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:1919 deaths Category:American male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of the United States Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Pottsville, Pennsylvania
